##################    EagleEye Overview of Cyber Security Study    ################


NIST Cybersecurity Framework 5 core functions:  ### Shortcut: "IPDRR" 

Identify – Understand risks (assets, threats, policies).
Protect – Safeguard systems (access control, training, encryption).
Detect – Find threats early (monitoring, anomalies).
Respond – Act during/after incidents (containment, reporting).
Recover – Restore operations (backups, lessons learned).
